----- Original Message -----
From: mamaaj2000
To: unschoolingbasics@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Thursday, July 08, 2004 08:36
Subject: [unschoolingbasics] Factory Tours web site


Mikey told me he wants to see where cars are made! I started
researching and found a cool web site: http://factorytourusa.com that
has 400+ factory tours across the country.

There's a RV assembly plant in Maryland, but they say kids 12 and
over only so I'll keep looking!

--aj
